    signal RXP ~ pin 6
    AVDD ~ pin 8
    AGND ~ pin 9
    signal EXRES1 ~ pin 10
    AVDD ~ pin 11
    AGND ~ pin 14
    AVDD ~ pin 15
    AGND ~ pin 16
    AVDD ~ pin 17
    signal VBG ~ pin 18
    AGND ~ pin 19
    signal TOCAP ~ pin 20
    AVDD ~ pin 21
    signal _1V2O ~ pin 22
    signal SPDLED ~ pin 24
    signal LINKLED ~ pin 25
    signal DUPLED ~ pin 26
    signal ACTLED ~ pin 27
    signal VDD ~ pin 28
    signal GND ~ pin 29
